# Terraform state — may contain plaintext secret values; local-only.
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/tfplan*.binary

# tfvars are sensitive — deployment-specific config (project IDs, URLs,
# regions, naming) changes per deployment and is NOT committed; the repo is
# cloned by many people. Commit ONLY the .example templates.
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example

# GCP service-account key files. Broad rule + anchored defense-in-depth so a
# real key stays ignored even if *.json is ever narrowed.
*.json
/labops-389703.json
/*-*.json
**/*-sa.json
**/sa-*.json
